Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:18.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima boku wa boku no tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do it for my own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kimi wa kimi no tame ni sou darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you do yours, don't we?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kakugo wa dekiteiru sa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm ready for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:32.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}toki ni tayoriaeru youna sonzai ni sasaerare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the support of someone I can rely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:39.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}souzou wo koeta mirai tsukamitore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seize the future beyond your imagination{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:45.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}iza te wo nobashite kaze wo kirisaite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach out your hand, cut through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:51.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kurayami wo kettobashite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kick away the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade mo yukeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll go wherever we wanna go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}namida mo mayoi mo isso hikitsurete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears and doubts in tow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:04.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}onore no iro de egaite yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's paint it in our own colors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominate it by forcing its people to labor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you open the borders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Robin was fighting Black Maria\Nin the castle, however...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet memories ruin you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I've left you alone\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tres Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come the Illusion Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come it didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...alongside my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Slash the Nightmare -\NBrook Draws His Freezing Sword!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me\Nif it wasn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for caring, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they mess with people's memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Black Maria-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s\NIllusion Mist didn't affect either of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She beat up her own mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wretched of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let down your parent,\Nthe people you owe, and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you privilege your own life that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not affected by it, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Illusion Mist thing is so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I? Bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've changed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering whose bones you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Captain Yorky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as you thought, I'm Captain Yorky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gather up all of the crew!\NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sea wind blows to where, who knows?\NThe waves will be our guide!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O'er across the ocean's tide,\Nthe sunset is goin' wild{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See the sky!\NBirds singing in circles passing by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bid farewell to weaver's town!\NSay so long to port renowne{\i0}d!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sing a song, it won't be long\Nbefore we're casting off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cross the gold and silver waves,\Nchangin' into water sprays!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sailing out on our journey\Nto the ends of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My beloved Rumbar Pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's smitten with you the most, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he likes music!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That my crewmates are all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'll never be able to see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...breaks my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I no longer have a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Song of Scratches...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blizzard Slice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna show me anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least show me your panties\Nrather than an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I won't let you flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she do such a terrible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not okay but I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 50 years, in the mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept wishing that the deaths\Nof my crewmates were a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw visions every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and felt hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have so much in common!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every ordeal was for the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so very happy to be alive!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because today came!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my friends' sake,\NI can't stay depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit is unbreakable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanyudo Sleeve Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That weird weapon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,WANYUDO - PUG SMILE FRUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say illusions don't affect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming that you can defeat Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop,\Nfire will spread throughout the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worrying about our castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you surrender yourself already?\NNico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0},\Ncould you keep holding me for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that weapon is a living thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanyudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being hot or too hot is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceburn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so close. Thanks, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nyou were sold out by your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black-Leg called you in front of me\Nknowing that you were my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're targeted\Nby such big names across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're a liability to your crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he called you in so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black-Leg is the laughingstock\Nof the whole of Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bounty is the second highest\Nin your group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shows how weak you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was very funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}! May I leave her to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the other creatures to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared of ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why he asked for my help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man worthy of being\None of the two arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigante Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pissed off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know\Nyou could make yourself so huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But looks like it's exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over before you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Serpent Snapdragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna get caught\Nwithout putting up a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your real body gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nit's good that the target is big!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And has many arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're big, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison barbs at the ends of my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-Nette!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onigashima is moving farther away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it falls onto the Flower Capital,\Nthe Land of Wano will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! I need more meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TOKAGE PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bring more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already eaten\Nall the provisions on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think\Nwe can find meat around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! I need more meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, his vitality is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can believe he's barely alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I thought you guys were on Onigashima.\N--How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked him up in the sea?\NHow's that for a miracle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we heard a voice in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We turned in that direction\Nand found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffytaro's voice?\NIs that what Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0} heard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! How lucky you are!\NYou are really alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came falling, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we got away from Kaido\Nwith Shinobu's kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To let me flee, in front of my very eyes,\NKiku and Kin'emon were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kikunojo of the Fallen Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't live any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let you get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get rid of you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for later!\NYou've always been like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the commander-in-chief!\NIt's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we kick Kaido's ass, it's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffytaro! Don't be so harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop crying, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the future Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you we don't have anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We're gonna go find some!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat's getting weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a bad sign, isn't it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he dies now,\NI'll be in so much trouble!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you'll do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna do the jailbreak thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't win,\NI can't get out of this country!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still gonna eat a ridiculous amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice. It'll take some time,\Nbut let's go to a nearby town to get some...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this is what you guys want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform into a dragon and fly me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Maria's wicked verbal attacks\Nweaken Robin's spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As she falls prey to a raging hellfire\Nand has both her body and soul burned to ash,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will it be light or darkness that blooms?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The roar that she raises for her loved ones\Nleads her to the black flower!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Clutch! A Demon Incarnate, Robin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,